overview: Kiara catches her step-mom Serene watching porn in her bedroom. What happens next will make bedtime a lot more fun from now on.  Chloe is working as a cam girl when her step-mother Katie walks in on her. Her fans convince Katie to join in and the money starts pouring in. Jill just started dating Kenna and really wants her step-mom Sarah to like her. They talk for a bit then Sarah suggests a way they can all get closer...  Gianna hears her dad and step-mother arguing in their room. Concerned that they'll get divorced, Gianna steps in to give India reasons to stay.
title: Mommy's Daughter
